  "instructions": [
    "Place the beef in a large pot. Sprinkle with thyme, salt, and pepper.",
    "In another pan, heat olive oil over medium-high heat. Add garlic and sauté until golden brown, about 2 minutes.",
    "Pour tomato paste into the pot with the beef. Gradually add broth, stirring to combine.",
    "Add the sautéed garlic mixture to the pot, then bring to a simmer. Cover and cook for 30-45 minutes or until the beef is tender.",
    "Serve hot with crusty bread."
